OL,4,Chealth issues'
OL,6,FThe ombudsman has asked Parliament to
OL,7,Fintervene and "act swiftly" to make
OL,8,Fsure a compensation scheme is
OL,9,Festablished.
OL,11,FWaspi campaigners had called for
OL,12,Fcompensation of #10,000 for all 3.8
OL,13,Fmillion women, but the report
OL,14,Frecommends between #1,000 and #2,950.
OL,16,F"It's a step in the right direction,
OL,17,Fbut it's not enough", says Liz.
