OL,6,F"There are going to be an awful lot of
OL,7,Fpeople who are struggling with the
OL,8,Fcost of living crisis, they've already
OL,9,Fhad to downsize their homes, they've
OL,10,Falready had to sell off their assets."
OL,12,F"Some ladies have even been sleeping
OL,13,Fin cars and using food banks so this
OL,14,Fis going to be no relief to them at
OL,15,Fall", she adds.
OL,17,FLiz says the changes mean many women
OL,18,Fhave not only suffered financially,
OL,19,Fbut mentally and physically too.
