OL,4,Chealth issues'
OL,6,F"I've been through an awful lot of
OL,7,Ftrauma. I've suffered redundancy, low
OL,8,Fwages, various serious health issues",
OL,9,Fexplains Liz.
OL,11,F"I think what PHSO should have done
OL,12,Fwas recommend something a lot higher,
OL,13,Fto take into account how long we've
OL,14,Fwaited, to take into account what
OL,15,Fwe've lost and to take into account
OL,16,Fwhat the government didn't offer us in
OL,17,Fthe first place."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/13
