OL,4,Chealth issues'
OL,6,F"They offered no alternative, they
OL,7,Foffered no sympathy, they've never
OL,8,Foffered any compassion. They've
OL,9,Fignored us, they've treated us like
OL,10,Fthey don't exist and it's been
OL,11,Fshambolic really, it's been
OL,12,Fdisgraceful."
