OL,4,Chealth issues'
OL,6,F"If the shoe was on the other foot, I
OL,7,Fmean they've treated men totally
OL,8,Fdifferent. Ladies from the 50s, the
OL,9,FWASPIS, we were impacted from 2011.
OL,10,FThe men weren't impacted until 2016
OL,11,Fand they only had their increase after
OL,12,Fone year. It was nothing to do with
OL,13,Fequality. It was absolutely shocking.
OL,14,FAnd as i say people are still finding
OL,15,Fout now."
