OL,3,CWaspi: 'Redundancy, low wages, serious
OL,4,Chealth issues'
OL,6,F"People who haven't got access to
OL,7,Finternet and stuff like that, they're
OL,8,Fcoming up to the age and they're
OL,9,Fthinking they're going to retire at 60
OL,10,Fbut they're going to have a damn big
OL,11,Fshock", she adds.
OL,13,FTo date, the has not acknowledged its
OL,14,Ffailings, nor put things right for
OL,15,Fthose affected, the report said.
OL,17,FThe report found the DWP's handling of
OL,18,Fthe pension age changes meant some
OL,19,Fwomen lost opportunities to make
OL,20,Finformed decisions about their
OL,21,Ffinances.
