OL,6,FIt diminished their sense of personal
OL,7,Fautonomy and financial control, the
OL,8,Fombudsman said.
OL,10,FPHSO chief executive Rebecca
OL,11,FHilsenrath said: "The UK's national
OL,12,Fombudsman has made a finding of
OL,13,Ffailings by DWP in this case, and has
OL,14,Fruled that the women affected are owed
OL,15,Fcompensation.
OL,17,F"DWP has clearly indicated that it
OL,18,Fwill refuse to comply. This is
OL,19,Funacceptable. The department must do
OL,20,Fthe right thing and it must be held to
OL,21,Faccount for failure to do so.
