OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F377A1711351967
OL,3,CWaspi: 'Redundancy, low wages, serious
OL,4,Chealth issues'
OL,6,F"Complainants should not have to wait
OL,7,Fand see whether DWP will take action
OL,8,Fto rectify its failings.
OL,10,F"Given the significant concerns we
OL,11,Fhave that it will fail to act on our
OL,12,Ffindings, and given the need to make
OL,13,Fthings right for the affected women as
OL,14,Fsoon as possible, we have proactively
OL,15,Fasked Parliament to intervene and hold
OL,16,Fthe department to account.
