OL,6,F"Parliament now needs to act swiftly,
OL,7,Fand make sure a compensation scheme is
OL,8,Festablished. We think this will
OL,9,Fprovide women with the quickest route
OL,10,Fto remedy."
OL,12,FThe ombudsman published stage one of
OL,13,Fits investigation in July 2021. It
OL,14,Ffound failings in the way DWP
OL,15,Fcommunicated changes to women's state
OL,16,Fpension age.
