OL,6,FSpeaking before the report's release,
OL,7,FHealth Minister Andrea Leadsom said:
OL,8,F"I've had a number of constituents of
OL,9,Fmy own who've talked to me about this
OL,10,Fover the years, and I do completely
OL,11,Funderstand the issue".
OL,13,FLabour's Shadow Work and Pensions
OL,14,FMinister Alison McGovern said: "When
OL,15,Fyou're planning for your retirement
OL,16,Ffuture, you need to understand what
OL,17,Fyou state pension entitlement is going
OL,18,Fto be, and if there are changes the
OL,19,Fgovernment has a responsibility to
OL,20,Fdeal with properly".
